Joshua Finbow, 23, a submarine engineer, Craig Stoner, 24, and Darren Smalley, 35, were given identical bail conditions .
They were charged with the rape of a woman at an ice hockey game in Halifax, Nova Scotia, on April 10 .
Bail conditions could see them have to live on a Canadian naval base for the next few years .
All four men will continue to work for the Royal Navy and draw their current pay .